  • Enclosing class:
    NetworkSecurityGrpc
    public static final class NetworkSecurityGrpc.NetworkSecurityBlockingStub
extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractBlockingStub<NetworkSecurityGrpc.NetworkSecurityBlockingStub>
    A stub to allow clients to do synchronous rpc calls to service NetworkSecurity. 
     Network Security API provides resources to configure authentication and
 authorization policies. Refer to per API resource documentation for more
 information.
